  <div class="card" id="format-convention">
    <h2 class="section-title">Format recommandé &amp; convention</h2>
    <p>Convention de commits : <a href="https://www.conventionalcommits.org/">Conventional Commits</a> en anglais — <code>&lt;type&gt;(&lt;scope&gt;): &lt;description&gt;</code></p>
    <ul class="list-tight">
      <li><strong>Date / Version</strong> : format SemVer (ex. 1.0.0, 0.5.0).</li>
      <li><strong>Types</strong> : <code>feat</code>, <code>fix</code>, <code>docs</code>, <code>test</code>, <code>chore</code>, <code>refactor</code>, <code>ci</code>, <code>perf</code>.</li>
      <li><strong>Scopes</strong> : <code>auth</code>, <code>stripe</code>, <code>booking</code>, <code>e2e</code>, <code>a11y</code>, <code>prisma</code>, <code>docs</code>, <code>search</code>, <code>messaging</code>.</li>
      <li><strong>Détails</strong> : tests ajoutés, couverture, contrôles sécurité/a11y, sections doc modifiées.</li>
      <li><strong>Références</strong> : tickets / PR / liens vers rapports tests.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Exemples de commits conformes :</strong></p>
    <ul class="list-tight">
      <li><code>feat(auth): add Google OAuth provider with NextAuth</code></li>
      <li><code>fix(stripe): handle webhook signature verification failure</code></li>
      <li><code>test(e2e): add payment flow tests with Playwright</code></li>
      <li><code>perf(search): add Redis cache layer for search results (TTL 5min)</code></li>
      <li><code>docs(mut): add OWASP Top 10 coverage table</code></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

